{"title":"All-new classic road Cervélo R5 Disc drops tons of weight, nearing 700g!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/29/all-new-classic-road-cervelo-r5-disc-drops-tons-of-weight-nearing-700g/","date":1632926700000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095758/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_zoom-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;zoom\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095758/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_zoom-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095758/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_zoom-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095758/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_zoom-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095758/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_zoom-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095758/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_zoom-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095758/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_zoom.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-273033\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Cervélo’s lightweight R5 Disc classic road bike hadn’t seen a major overhaul since the third generation of the bike more than <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2017/06/16/cervelo-r-series-road-bikes-reinvented-lighter-stiffer-aero-race-machines/\">four years ago</a>. But now a new 2022 R5 Disc is back with a vengeance, going on 16% weight-loss diet in this gen 4 to shed a full 130g, making it an even better all-rounder at a claimed 703g, almost unmatched even among the lightest climbers-only bikes…</p><h2>2022 Cervélo R5 Disc carbon road bike gets even lighter!</h2><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/f-2fdzESFVI?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>The new Cervélo R5 Disc was developed with the Jumbo-Visma pros to be lightweight foremost, ensuring the team would always get their race bikes down to the 6.8kg UCI limit without having to cut corners on equipment like power meters or the ideal wheel &amp; tire choice of the day.</p><p>But neither Cervelo nor the pro riders were willing to sacrifice on the World Tour-proven race performance of the R5 that has made it just as strong a descender as a climber.</p><div id=\"attachment_273079\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095753/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Spring-Classics.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273079\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095753/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Spring-Classics.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;Spring Classics\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095753/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Spring-Classics.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095753/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Spring-Classics-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095753/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Spring-Classics-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095753/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Spring-Classics-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095753/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Spring-Classics-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273079\">all photos c. Cervélo</p></div><p>And now having been raced this season in the Spring Classics, then ridden to a mountain stage win at this year’s Tour de France, together with an overall Vuelta GC win, it’s once again an undeniably versatile all-rounder.</p><div id=\"attachment_273078\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273078\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;Vuelta winner\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095749/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_2021-Vuelta-win-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273078\">2021 Vuelta a España winner Primož Roglič</p></div><h3>What’s new? Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;frame\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095745/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_black-frameset-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>From its outward profile, the new R5 Disc looks quite similar to the bike that it replaces. But deeper integration &amp; smoother lines redefine the new race bike. Up front are the most obvious changes, starting with a new smooth aero transition from the lower fork crown into the downtube, which now sits a bit closer to the front tire.</p><p>Inside the layup Cervelo says there’s plenty of carbon optimization, but overall power transfer &amp; lateral stiffness of the frame is said to be the same as before – one of the first incidences of the new bike’s “don’t mess with what works” development approach.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;angled\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095741/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_SRAM-angled-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>There was however a concerted effort to make the front end more comfortable, as pro riders noted that the previous R5 fork was probably too stiff, to the point that it was wearing them down over the course of a Grand Tour. Part of that comfort comes from refined layup, but also new bigger tire clearances.</p><p>Much like the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/07/23/all-new-cervelo-caledonia-is-a-modern-road-bike-w-big-tire-clearance-built-for-roubaix/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">aero road Caledonia</a> that launched last summer, the new R5 Disc has room&nbsp;for up to 34mm wide tires making this a true Spring Classics-ready race bike. (Compared that to the 30mm clearance of the old R5, which had necessitated the rare old <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2012/10/16/found-cervelo-r3-mud-extremely-limited-edition-cobble-racer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">R3 Mud</a>)</p><p>Of course, complete integration also means a new fully internal cable routing setup through the upper headset cup that also brings some bonus aero gains, as well.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;seatpost clamp detail\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp-297x186.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp-800x500.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp-120x75.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095738/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_seatpost-clamp-1536x960.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Extending the mix of rider comfort AND integration, a new trimmed down wedge clamp secures the D-shaped seatpost which now tucks inside the top of the seatstays, getting rid of the small cap over the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2017/06/16/cervelo-r-series-road-bikes-reinvented-lighter-stiffer-aero-race-machines/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">old R5</a>‘s seat cluster.</p><p>Adding all of those little details together, and the new R5 Disc claims a weight of just 703g for a 56cm painted frame, plus another 328g for the fork.</p><p>That’s surprisingly close to the super limited edition original 700g <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2010/02/22/cervelos-new-ultralight-project-california-road-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">R5ca</a> or more recent 667g <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2013/03/14/new-667g-cervelo-rca-road-bike-delivers-less-weight-more-tech-same-stiffness/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">RCA</a>, both of which were still on rim brakes only and were framesets that sold for 2x as much as this new R5 Disc.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095734/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_new-cockpit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095734/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_new-cockpit.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;cockpit\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095734/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_new-cockpit.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095734/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_new-cockpit-297x149.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095734/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_new-cockpit-800x400.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095734/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_new-cockpit-120x60.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095734/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_new-cockpit-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Looking at the rest of the new R5’s components, its new seatpost itself apparently sheds another 20g. And the separate new aero, ergonomic Cervelo carbon bar &amp; stem add up to another 24g weight savings, too.</p><p>All in, the new bike features a tapered 1.25-1.5″ FSA headset to route cables internally, a BBRight bottom bracket, flat mount disc brakes, and 12mm thru-axles with QR removable levers.</p><h3>Road Race Geometry only slightly tweaked</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;racing\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095731/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_world-tour-proven-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Geometry on the new Cervelo R5 Disc is effectively unchanged, +/-1mm from the previous generation as the Jumbo-Visma pro riders essentially said not to mess with a good thing (<em>again</em>). The only real functional change in the stock six size range (48-61cm) was apparently a tiny bit of extra fork trail (0.3mm) said to compensate for the larger size tires riders are racing these days.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;geometry\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry-297x165.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry-800x444.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry-768x427.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095727/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_tweaked-road-race-geometry-1536x853.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p>The bikes do get taller headtubes that balance out with the shorter fork crown heights to come out at effectively the same frame Stack &amp; Reach figures. And newly more sloping toptube layout does yield lower standover heights for the larger frame sizes, though.</p><h3>Cervélo R5 Disc – Pricing &amp; options</h3><div id=\"attachment_273070\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273070\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;frameset\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset-297x186.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset-800x500.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset-120x75.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095723/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_Jumbo-Visma-team-replica-frameset-1536x960.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273070\">2022 Cervélo R5 frameset Disc</p></div><p>The new Cervélo R5 is now disc brake-only and sells for $5000 as a frameset (frame, fork, seatpost, bar, stem, headset &amp; axles) in any of three colors: Five Black, replica Jumbo-Visma Black/Gold (<em>above</em>), and Lime/Black (<em>below</em>).</p><div id=\"attachment_273069\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273069\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;SRAM Force AXS\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095720/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-force-etap-lime-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273069\">2022 Cervélo R5 Force eTap AXS Disc</p></div><p>Three complete bike build options are available now, including the “entry” $8400 / 8800€ SRAM Force eTap AXS 2×12 bike with a power meter crankset and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/06/30/reserve-carbon-wheels-venture-into-road-deeper-gravel-with-cervelo-aftermarket-comes-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Reserve</a> tubeless carbon wheels on Zipp hubs. (A new Ultegra Di2 build is expected at a similar pricepoint.)</p><div id=\"attachment_273068\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273068\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;Shimano Dura-Ace Di2\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095716/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_R5-Dura-Ace-Di2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273068\">2022 Cervélo R5 Dura-Ace Di2 Disc</p></div><p>Going to the extreme high-end, two ultra premium builds sell for essentially the same $12,000 / 12,000€ pricetag. Shimano fans can get new Dura-Ace Di2 2×12 with CermmicSpeed bearings and <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/06/30/reserve-carbon-wheels-venture-into-road-deeper-gravel-with-cervelo-aftermarket-comes-next/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Reserve carbon wheels</a> on DT 240 hubs.</p><div id=\"attachment_273067\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-273067\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;SRAM Red AXS\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs.jpg 1800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095711/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_r5-red-etap-axs-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-273067\">2022 Cervélo R5 Red eTap AXS Disc</p></div><p>Or for that same $12,000, SRAM fans can swap in a complete Red eTap AXS wireless 2×12 build including a carbon Red powermeter crankset, and the same Reserve wheels.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095707/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_dolomites-riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095707/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_dolomites-riding.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Cervelo R5 Disc lightweight carbon all-rounder classic road bike,&nbsp;riding DOlomites\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095707/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_dolomites-riding.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095707/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_dolomites-riding-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095707/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_dolomites-riding-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095707/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_dolomites-riding-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/29095707/2022-Cervelo-R5-Disc-lightweight-carbon-all-rounder-classic-road-bike_dolomites-riding-768x461.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.cervelo.com/en/r5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Cervelo.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d6fef70a0c2f75861f74bd20cc05743169f90b0a9154e282a7bc2e9c5ebd5089","category":"Cycling"}